name: At the Moment
overview: This anthology series set during the pandemic follows 10 unique love stories of passion and heartache.

episodes.name: Reality Dating Show
episodes.overview: After a sweet encounter at an audition, Hsia Wei-ting joins a reality show and finds herself caught up in a whirlwind of fame and scripted romances.

episodes.name: The Night in Question
episodes.overview: Two wounded souls, a single mother and a delivery worker from Hong Kong, cross paths at a massage parlor during a fateful night of misadventures.

episodes.name: The Color of You
episodes.overview: A charming hairstylist develops feelings for a blind woman he meets on the subway. However, some secrets could disrupt their budding romance.

episodes.name: From Beyond the Stars
episodes.overview: Trapped at home, romance writer Yao Chih-hsuan is sure she's an accidental time traveler. No one believes her — except a mysterious neighbor.

episodes.name: The Perfect Dodgeball Game
episodes.overview: When Chia-hao discovers his new intern is homeless, he offers him a place to stay. As they share the same roof, their bond quickly gets complicated.

episodes.name: Something Old
episodes.overview: When Fang Jo-nan finds herself without a job or home, she turns to her ex-boyfriend Joe for help. But the shadows of their past quickly reemerge.

episodes.name: The Promise of Karuizawa
episodes.overview: Chang Wei-hsi meets Chao Ting-yu while tracking their respective unfaithful spouses. Soon after, they must confront their own moral conundrums.

episodes.name: Head of the Family
episodes.overview: A pandemic forces a couple to swap their traditional home duties — until a family member with old-fashioned views shows up at their door.

episodes.name: The Ghost in Your Heart
episodes.overview: Lost in grief, news anchor Lo Hsin-lan unexpectedly reconnects with a high school friend, unearthing memories of a love that was once taboo.

episodes.name: Based on True Events
